{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10108598999203-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10108598999203-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100123221957-1","P_10100123221957-2","P_10100123221957-3","P_10100123221957-4"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":2,"description":"阅读文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":174,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>爱祖国的宋庆龄</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">1908年，15岁的宋庆龄在美国留学。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">她是一位热爱祖国、喜欢沉思、学习勤奋<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">的女孩子。</span>有一天，班里讨论有关历史方面的问题，她认真搜集资料，认真思索，做了充分准备。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">讨论时，一位美国学生站起来说：“我认为，历史的发展是难以估计的。你们看，那些所谓的文明古国，特别是亚洲的中国，已经被历史淘汰了。人类的希望在欧洲，在美洲，在我们这里……”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">宋庆龄摇了摇头，耐心地听完了这位同学的发言。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">那位同学讲完话，宋庆龄立即站起来，显得有些激动，但仍然用柔和的声调说：“历史确实是不断变化的，但它永远属于亿万大众。具有五千年文明历史的中国，没有被淘汰，也不可能被淘汰。<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">有人说中国像一头沉睡的狮子，但它决不会永远沉睡下去。有多少革命志士为它的振兴进行着艰苦卓绝的斗争！有一天，这头睡狮的吼声必将震动全世界！</span>因为它有广阔的土地，有众多的人口，有悠久的历史，有富饶的物产，有革命的传统……”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">“哗——”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">教室里响起了热烈的掌声，大家交口称赞：“说得好，以理服人。”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">宋庆龄时时刻刻关心着国内的情况。有时，她在学校的刊物上发表关于中国社会和前途的文章，深受老师和同学的赞许。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">有一位同学问她：“你为什么总想着什么祖国呀，什么大众啊……”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">宋庆龄听了，眨了眨那明亮的宝石似的眼睛，抿着嘴笑了笑，说：“我不能忘掉祖国，我对我的祖国充满了希望。一个人，如果真的忘记了祖国，那人生该是多么没有意义啊！”</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"听了傲慢的美国同学的发言，宋庆龄显得有些激动，但她为什么仍然用柔和的声调说呢？（　）","answers":[{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"因为宋庆龄觉得美国同学的发言很有道理。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"因为中国是一个讲礼仪的国家，宋庆龄代表的不仅是自己，还代表着中国人的形象。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"对短文中画线的句子，正确的理解是（　）","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"中国不会永远落后，有许多革命志士在为它的振兴而努力，有朝一日，它会震惊世界。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"中国已经被历史淘汰。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisL